        <h4 class="modal-title">About us!</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p> We all as a team worked on this project together, each having a different, but nonetheless important roles:</p>
        <p>Neena Dugar- Role in the back end team, for Hide + Street, (the game), she did the random point generation algorithm.</p>
        <p>Andrew Deniszczyc- Role in both the back end team + the front end team, for Hide + Street, (the game), he did the Street View API integration.</p>
        <p>Leah Shields- Role in the back end team, for Hide + Street, (the game), she did the end point generation.</p>
        <p>Oliver Johnson- Role in both the back end team and the front end team, for Hide + Street, (the game and layout of page), he did the hot and cold sensor and the logo.</p>
        <p>Joel Knowles- Role in the front end team, for Hide + Street, (the webpage design), he did the logo, wireframes and fonts and colours.</p>
        <p>Neel Dugar- Role in the front end team, for Hide + Street (the main webpage), he did the basic webpage code, and the fonts and colours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
